Early Access Review

Well ... I really enjoyed this game. For a long time I've been looking for a survival of this genre but have yet to add and improve some things (I know some have been said in reviews of other players but I will stress again) .:
- Variety of aquatic species, terrestrial species and birds;
- Improvements in aquatic environments;
- Larger and closer Islands;
- New sounds;
- I think we could add a few more craftables;
- More places to explore.
(the time I played this game does not let me give more ideas)
In my opinion these game would be good even if the island was much higher, thus allowing the addition of rivers, predators, greater variety of plants, ravines, caves, most other animals that would fit with the environment ....)
THIS GAME HAS A HUGE POTENTIAL. PLEASE DEEM YOUR BEST TO DEVELOP THIS SURVIVAL.
Thank you for creating this game and good work :)

(I used google translator to do this review. I apologize if any collapse in writing)

