Early Access Review

Buy this game if:
-you like underwater exploration, survival, or Cast Away;
-you can tolerate Early Access bugs;
-graphics are important to you.

Don't buy this game if:
-you are expecting frequent and big updates;
-you hate buggy games;
-you are looking for a very difficult game.
